# Core Module Directory
#
# This directory contains the core business logic and services layer.
#
# Build Map v2.1 ENHANCED compliance:
# - All services extend CoreService abstract base
# - Structured error handling with BizError
# - Contextual logging with Logger interface
# - MariaDB 10.11 database operations
# - API standardization with apiHandler wrapper
#
# Architecture boundaries:
# - Core can import: Standard libraries, Next.js framework
# - Core cannot import: app, components, features, lib layers
# - All errors must use BizError class
# - Services must follow CoreService pattern
#
# Subdirectories:
# - services/     - Business logic services (DatabaseService, ApiService, etc.)
# - errors/       - Error handling classes (BizError)
# - logging/      - Logging interfaces and implementations
# - types/        - Type definitions and interfaces
# - api/          - API utilities and handlers (apiHandler)
# - utils/        - Core utility functions
# - hooks/        - Core React hooks
# - config/       - Configuration management
#
# BUILD_V5.0 P1 Service Foundation implemented ✓